'''Kaha trees''' were a [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[Plant/Legends|plant]] native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Talasea]]. A former administrator of the [[Intergalactic Communications Center]] arranged for them to be imported to the [[planet]] [[Praesitlyn/Legends|Praesitlyn]].

